HEADWORD: Beach comber
<hw>Beach" comb`er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A long, curling wave
rolling in from the ocean. See <er>Comber</er>.</def> <mark>[Amer.,
archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
